<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Thymeleaf</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://bit.ly/3WJ5ilK" />
</head>
<body>
    <!-- m5.html -->
    <h1>콘텐츠 조작</h1>
    <!--
    
        <태그>내용물</태그>
        - PCDATA 조작     > innerText(textContent)
        - 자식 태그 조작  > innerHTML 
        
        Thymeleaf Text
        1. th:text
            - escaped text
            - innerText
        
        2. th:utext
            - unescaped text
            - innerHTML
            
        3. 인라인 출력
            모든 태그 th:inline값을 가진다.(생략)
            - th:inline="text"  //default
            - th:inline="javascript"
            
            - th:inline + [[]]
        
        
        
        <div th:text="값"></div>
        <div>값</div>
     
    -->
    <div th:text="${txt1}"></div>
    <div th:utext="${txt1}"></div>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div th:text="${txt2}"></div>
    <div th:utext="${txt2}"></div>
    
    
    
    
</body>
</html>





